Program: Start the Week
Title: Live from the Hay Festival
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b08rp2x0
Last Broadcast Date: Mon 29 May 2017
Tom Sutcliffe presents Start the Week live from the Hay Festival. He is joined by award winning authors Colm Tóibín, Sebastian Barry and Meg Rosoff to discuss how they breathe new life into stories from the past, from Greek tragedy to civil war, while the psychologist Jan Kizilhan explains how a history of trauma and genocide has been woven into the story of his Yazidi community. Producer: Katy Hickman. Show less